Modifications to speedtest-cli:
- This project includes a compatibility patch (fix_speedtest_py313.py) for
  Python 3.13 compatibility with Kivy environments
- The patch modifies error handling in the speedtest module to catch
  AttributeError in addition to OSError for sys.stderr.fileno()
